      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/nestle-s-struggling-shares-cast-shadow-over-schneider-s-tenure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雀巢公司 (Nestle SA) 近年来股价表现疲软，给马克施奈德 (Mark Schneider) 担任这家消费品巨头首席执行官期间蒙上了一层阴影。]]></description>
