      <title>克罗地亚将重点关注旅游租赁以应对住房紧缩问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/croatia-moves-to-target-tourism-rentals-to-tackle-housing-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚正寻求通过有效限制关键旅游业中私人公寓的租赁来解决欧盟国家的住房短缺问题，以使家庭更能负担得起居住空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/croatia-moves-to-target-tourism-rentals-to-tackle-housing-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
